  "body": "# Feature Issue\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to see a summary of my collectible transaction **so that** I can review the details and sign to confirm it.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nFigma Design: https://www.figma.com/file/HKncH4wnDwZDAhc4AryK8Y/Wallet-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=1355-317327&mode=design&t=nilAPUyk59K54DQh-4\r\n\r\nVisual reference:\r\n<img width=\"252\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/18485527/9fc62c80-7770-495f-bcad-cd6862543c9e\">\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\n- [x] Show title that specifies which collectible you are sending, from which account and who is the reciever \r\n- [x] Show `From` and `To` detail cards with collectible title\r\n- [x] Show `Details` card\r\n- [x] Show `Slide to sign` slider and add authentication process\r\n- [x] Execute transaction if the user slides and authentication succeeds\r\n- [x] Light and dark mode should be implemented\r\n- [x] Background gradient color should be based on account color",
